The paper deals with image understanding and natural language processing, which are both core topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of attention mechanisms and relation classification networks also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval, as it aligns entities in captions to objects in the image, which could fall under the sub-category of information retrieval (cs.IR).
